"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:5.4\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">5.4</span> 標題：火把（torch）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： לַפִּיד</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： lapid)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:17\">GEN 15:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg7:16\">JDG 7:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg7:20\">JDG 7:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg15:4\">JDG 15:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg15:4\">JDG 15:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg15:5\">JDG 15:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job41:11\">JOB 41:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa62:1\">ISA 62:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:13\">EZK 1:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:6\">DAN 10:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah2:5\">NAM 2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech12:6\">ZEC 12:6</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： δᾳδουχία</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： dadouchia)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc4:22\">2MA 4:22</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： λαμπάς</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： lampas)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:1\">MAT 25:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:4\">MAT 25:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:7\">MAT 25:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:8\">MAT 25:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:3\">JHN 18:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:8\">ACT 20:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:5\">REV 4:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev8:10\">REV 8:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt10:22\">JDT 10:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir48:1\">SIR 48:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc6:39\">1MA 6:39</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： φῶς</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： fōs)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:29\">ACT 16:29</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0475_torch.jpg\" alt=\"燃燒的火炬\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">燃燒的火炬 (© Andrew Dunn, CC BY-SA 2.0, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>火把是一根或一捆燃燒的棍子，可以拿著照明。為了延長燃燒的時間，棍子的一端可能會纏上一些浸泡過瀝青等易燃物的布。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>在現代英式英語中，“torch”（「火把」）是一種由電池供電的手持式電燈，也就是美式英語中的“flashlight”（「手電筒」）。但是，這樣的詞語在聖經翻譯中是完全不合適的。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job41:11\">JOB 41:11</a> （《和》41:19）：這裡的重點是火焰，而不是產生火焰的火把，因此這節經文的第一行可譯為，「火焰從牠口中噴出」（如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> ）。</p>\n<p>希臘文<em>lampas</em> 最準確的意思是「火把」。在有些經文中（如<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:8\">ACT 20:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:5\">REV 4:5</a> ），部分英文譯本使用了派生詞“lamp”（「燈」）。</p>\n<p>有些語言可能很難區分<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:3\">JHN 18:3</a> 中的「火把」和「燈籠」。在這種情況下，可譯為「燃燒著的木棍和內有小火苗的容器，用來照明」。另參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">5.3 燈籠 (lantern)&lt;REALIA:5.3&gt;</a> 中的討論。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:29\">ACT 16:29</a> ：獄警要求拿「光」來，但經文並沒有指明具體的照明工具。許多語言可以遵循<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 和<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"German Common Language Version (Gute Nachricht Bibel)\">GECL</abbr> 的做法，將這節經文的開頭譯作「獄警要求拿光來照亮」。監獄入口處的火把很可能是最方便拿到的。然而，譯為「獄警叫人拿燈來」也足以表達他的意圖。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
